+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
; Port Connectivity Checks: "riscv_cpu:rvcpu|datapath:dp|mux4:ResultMux"                                                                                                 ;
+------+-------+----------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
; Port ; Type  ; Severity ; Details                                                                                                                                      ;
+------+-------+----------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
